typeProperties.script:
source(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	query: 'select * from dwh_stage.',
	format: 'query',
	wildcardPaths:['Other/lloyds_vessel_history.parquet']) ~> lloydsvesselhistory
source(output(
		company_id as integer,
		telephone as string,
		post_code_2 as string,
		email as string,
		website as string,
		iso3 as string,
		company_status as string,
		country as string,
		town_city as string,
		company_first_year_qualifier as string,
		office_status as string,
		company_first_year as short,
		post_code_1 as string,
		audit_created as date,
		address_line_3 as string,
		address_line_2 as string,
		company_name as string,
		address_line_1 as string,
		address_line_4 as string,
		audit_updated as date,
		fax as string,
		county_state as string,
		snapshot_date as date,
		record_last_updated as date
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	query: 'select * from dwh_stage.lloyds_company',
	format: 'query') ~> lloydscompany
source(output(
		code_type_id as long,
		code2 as string,
		target_description as string,
		source_system as string,
		om_x_ref as string,
		target_code as string,
		code_type as string,
		source_code_key as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	query: 'select * from dwh_stage.t_crossreference',
	format: 'query') ~> tcrossreference
lloydsvesselhistory, manager lookup(TECHNICAL_MANAGER_ID == company_id_mgr,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> companyMgr
lloydscompany select(mapColumn(
		company_id_benOwner = COMPANY_ID,
		obj_gbo_owner = COMPANY_NAME
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> benificialOwner
lloydscompany select(mapColumn(
		company_id_comOper = COMPANY_ID,
		obj_operator = COMPANY_NAME
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> commercialOperator
lloydscompany select(mapColumn(
		company_id_regOwner = COMPANY_ID,
		obj_reg_owner = COMPANY_NAME
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> regOwner
lloydscompany select(mapColumn(
		company_id_mgr = COMPANY_ID,
		obj_manager = COMPANY_NAME
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> manager
companyMgr, benificialOwner lookup(BENEFICIAL_OWNER_ID == company_id_benOwner,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> companyGBowner
companyGBowner, commercialOperator lookup(COMMERCIAL_OPERATOR_ID == company_id_comOper,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> companyOperator
companyOperator, regOwner lookup(REGISTERED_OWNER_ID == company_id_regOwner,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> companyRegOwner
companyRegOwner, beneficialOwnerCountry lookup(BENEFICIAL_OWNER_ID == company_id_benOwnCtry,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> companyGBOwnerCnty
companyGBOwnerCnty, managerCountry lookup(TECHNICAL_MANAGER_ID == company_id_mgrCntry,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> companyMgrCnty
companyMgrCnty, operatorCountry lookup(COMMERCIAL_OPERATOR_ID == company_id_operCntry,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> companyOperatorCnty

		obj_fdwt = FORMULA_DWT,

		obj_depth = DEPTH,

		obj_date_dead = DEAD_DATE,
		obj_class1_code = CLASS1_CODE,

		obj_iceclass = CLASS1_ICE_CLASS,

		obj_class2_code = CLASS2_CODE,
		obj_class2 = CLASS2,
		obj_pandi_club_code = PI_CLUB_ID,
		obj_pandi_club = PI_CLUB,
		obj_total_kw = POWER_KW,

		obj_operator_country_code,
		obj_reg_owner_country_desc,
		obj_reg_owner_country
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> tmptabell
tmptabell derive(obj_gard_objectid = '',
		obj_flag_iso3 = '',
		obj_status = '',
		obj_class3 = '',
		obj_class3_code = '',
		obj_m3 = '',
		obj_ship_builder_country = '',
		obj_service_speed = '',
		obj_length_overall = '',
		obj_hullid = '',
		obj_date_built = '',
		obj_propeller_type_desc = '',
		obj_hull_type = '',
		obj_propulsion = '',
		obj_material_build = '',
		iceclass = '',
		iceclasstext = '',
		last_updated_by = 'pre_dim_object',
		lloyds_vessel_id = obj_sourceid) ~> derivedColumns
derivedColumns, xrefMarketArea lookup(obj_gbo_owner_country == source_code_key_xref_market,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> marketDesc
marketDesc, xrefCountry lookup(obj_gbo_owner_country == source_code_key_xref_country,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> countryDesc
countryDesc, xrefOTDesc lookup(obj_object_type_code == source_code_key_xref_OTDesc,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> objectTypeDesc
objectTypeDesc, xrefFlagDesc lookup(obj_flag_iso3_code == source_code_key_flagDesc,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> flagDesc
lloydscompany select(mapColumn(
		company_id_benOwnCtry = COMPANY_ID,
		obj_gb_owner_country_desc = COUNTRY,
		obj_gbo_owner_country = ISO3
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> beneficialOwnerCountry
lloydscompany select(mapColumn(
		company_id_mgrCntry = COMPANY_ID,
		obj_manager_country_desc = COUNTRY,
		obj_manager_country_code = ISO3
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> managerCountry
lloydscompany select(mapColumn(
		company_id_operCntry = COMPANY_ID,
		obj_operator_country_desc = COUNTRY,
		obj_operator_country_code = ISO3
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> operatorCountry

		obj_reg_owner_country_desc = COUNTRY,
		obj_reg_owner_country = ISO3
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> commercialOwnerCntry

	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> companyComOwnerCnty

		obj_market_area_country_code = TARGET_CODE,
		obj_market_area_country_desc = TARGET_DESCRIPTION

	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> xrefCountry

		source_code_key_xref_OTDesc = SOURCE_CODE_KEY,
		source_system_xref_OTDesc = SOURCE_SYSTEM,

		code_type_id_xref_OTDesc = CODE_TYPE_ID

	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,

		obj_rpm,
		obj_hp,
		obj_engine_builder,
		obj_engine_designation,
		obj_engine_designer,
		obj_num_of_cylinders,
		obj_cylinder_arrangement,
		obj_engine_type,
		obj_stroke_type,
		obj_fuel_type_code = obj_fuel_type,
		obj_manager_code,
		obj_date_valid_from,
		obj_date_valid_to,

		obj_market_area_code,

		obj_market_area_country_code,
		obj_market_area_country_desc
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> selectOutputColumn
flagDesc derive(obj_object_type = case(isNull(target_description_object_type), obj_object_type, target_description_object_type),
		obj_flag_iso3 = case(isNull(target_description_flag), obj_flag_iso3, target_description_flag)) ~> expression
selectOutputColumn alterRow(upsertIf(true())) ~> alterRow
tcrossreference filter(CODE_TYPE_ID==100 && SOURCE_SYSTEM=='LLOYDS') ~> flag
tcrossreference filter(CODE_TYPE_ID==45 && SOURCE_SYSTEM=='LLOYDS') ~> objectType
tcrossreference filter(CODE_TYPE_ID==50 && SOURCE_SYSTEM=='LLOYDS') ~> country
tcrossreference filter(CODE_TYPE_ID==806 && SOURCE_SYSTEM=='LLOYDS') ~> market
